Upper Sorbian spelling dictionary
=================================

Upper Sorbian dictionary for use with the Mozilla spell checker.

Słownik hornjoserbšćiny - prawopisna kontrola za Mozilla.

Upstream author: Prof. Dr. Eduard Werner
License: GNU General Public License (version 2 or later)


Description
===========

This extension is a spelling dictionary for Firefox, Thunderbird, and
Seamonkey. It can be downloaded from:

  <https://addons.mozilla.org/browse/type:3>

The upstream author is Prof. Dr. Eduard Werner (Edward Wornar).


